    INSTALL, CHANGELOG
Source-Repository head
    Type:     darcs
    Location: http://community.haskell.org/~wren/logfloat

----------------------------------------------------------------
Flag useFFI
    Default:     True
    Description: Use FFI to link C's log1p. Improves accuracy and
                 same performance. Disable only if your compiler
                 doesn't support FFI.

